message.entry: The delsample method can only be used for a single timeseries object
Indices must be specified by a vector of integers.
Specified indices are out of bounds.
Time must be a numeric value.
The time value cannot be converted to the timeseries format
The Value input must be a date character vector/string, cell array of date character vectors/strings, or numeric
You must specify a sample index or time to delete each sample.
The second argument must be a character vector/string specifying the method that identifies the samples to be deleted.
